Welcome Home!
Welcome to The Living Room, a cool spot where dining feels like kicking back in your own living room but with the bonus of fantastic food. The original Living Room was founded in 2008, but it really came into its own in 2015 when Zach and Christina Feinstein took over, reimagining it as a place where casual meets culinary excellence. Located in Dunedin and now also in Wesley Chapel, we blend the comfort of familiar dishes with creative twists that keep our menus exciting.
Our restaurants are all about relaxed vibes and great meals. The spaces are designed to feel like you're at a friend’s home—comfortable and inviting, perfect for lingering over a meal or having a drink. From the friendly service to the locally sourced ingredients, everything we do is about enhancing your dining experience.
Drop in to see why The Living Room is more than just a place to eat—it's where food and comfort come together to create a uniquely laid-back dining adventure. Whether you’re up for a chill brunch or a cozy dinner, we're here to make every visit special. Come by, enjoy the vibe, eat well, and see why our guests keep coming back.
